ol.li:
Create the file .java.login.config in the user home
            folder. For example, on a Linux system, the home folder is similar to
              /home/gpadmin. 
Add the following text to the
            file:pgjdbc {
  com.sun.security.auth.module.Krb5LoginModule required
  doNotPrompt=true
  useTicketCache=true
  ticketCache = "C:\\Users\\gpadmin\\cache.txt"
  debug=true
  client=true;
};
